BC
E
 \sin \beta = \dfrac{|AE|}{|AB|} \qquad \text{and} \qquad \sin \gamma = \dfrac{|AE|}{|AC|} 
 |AB|\sin\beta=|AE|=|AC|\sin\gamma 
